{
  "texts": [
    "Ov3 15 differs from YOLOv2 in that it employs DarkNet53 as a feature extraction network and FPN to handle multi-scale detection difficulties.",
    "However, there are issues with incorrect positioning.",
    "Ov4 16 was proposed as a result of this.",
    "It has made significant changes and performs well when compared to the previous edition.",
    "Then there were YOLOv5, YOLOv7 17, and YOLOv8."
  ]
}